{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/suspension/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Developer's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"25f2934c-b1a3-5151-95a1-d524601f6643","excerpt":"Meaning “Suspension” refers to the act of stopping or delaying something temporarily, or the state of being stopped or delayed.\nIt can also refer to a system…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#meaning\">Meaning</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\">Grammar and Usage</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#main-usages\">Main Usages:</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#common-phrases\">Common Phrases</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#collocations\">Collocations</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\">Synonyms or Related</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#antonym\">Antonym</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<h2 id=\"meaning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#meaning\" aria-label=\"meaning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Meaning</h2>\n<p><em>“Suspension”</em> refers to the act of stopping or delaying something temporarily, or the state of being stopped or delayed.\nIt can also refer to a system that absorbs shocks (as in a car), or a liquid mixture where particles are dispersed but not dissolved.</p>\n<h2 id=\"grammar-and-usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\" aria-label=\"grammar and usage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grammar and Usage</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Part of speech:</strong> noun</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Countable/Uncountable:</strong> can be both</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Common structures:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>the suspension of + noun</em> (e.g., the suspension of service)</li>\n<li><em>under suspension</em> (e.g., The player is under suspension.)</li>\n<li><em>suspension system</em> (technical use for vehicles)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"main-usages\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#main-usages\" aria-label=\"main usages permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Main Usages:</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Temporary stop or delay</strong>\n→ <em>The suspension of the project</em> means the project is paused.</li>\n<li><strong>Punishment at work or school</strong>\n→ <em>He was given a three-day suspension.</em></li>\n<li><strong>Mechanical system (cars, bikes)</strong>\n→ <em>The car’s suspension needs repair.</em></li>\n<li><strong>Scientific term (chemistry)</strong>\n→ <em>A suspension of particles in a liquid.</em></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"common-phrases\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#common-phrases\" aria-label=\"common phrases permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common Phrases</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>under suspension</strong> – temporarily banned or not allowed to work</li>\n<li><strong>suspension bridge</strong> – a bridge supported by cables</li>\n<li><strong>suspension system</strong> – part of a vehicle that absorbs shocks</li>\n<li><strong>temporary suspension</strong> – short-term pause or halt</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"collocations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collocations\" aria-label=\"collocations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collocations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>service suspension</strong></li>\n<li><strong>license suspension</strong></li>\n<li><strong>school suspension</strong></li>\n<li><strong>project suspension</strong></li>\n<li><strong>bridge suspension system</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>The company announced the <strong>suspension of flights</strong> due to bad weather.</li>\n<li>The student received a <strong>three-day suspension</strong> for breaking the rules.</li>\n<li>Engineers inspected the <strong>car’s suspension system</strong> after the accident.</li>\n<li>The <strong>temporary suspension</strong> of talks disappointed many supporters.</li>\n<li>The scientist examined a <strong>suspension of sand particles in water.</strong></li>\n<li>The officer was placed <strong>under suspension</strong> pending investigation.</li>\n<li>The <strong>suspension bridge</strong> swayed slightly in the wind.</li>\n<li>The government lifted the <strong>suspension of visa services</strong> last week.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"synonyms-or-related\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\" aria-label=\"synonyms or related permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Synonyms or Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>interruption</li>\n<li>halt</li>\n<li>pause</li>\n<li>delay</li>\n<li>stoppage</li>\n<li>expulsion (in school contexts)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"antonym\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#antonym\" aria-label=\"antonym permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Antonym</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>continuation</li>\n<li>resumption</li>\n<li>restoration</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"suspension meaning and examples","date":"2025-10-26","description":"English learning materials; suspension explanation.","tags":["English","noun"],"featuredImage":{"publicURL":"/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/suspension.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8e8d8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/b5658/suspension.png","srcSet":"/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/acb7c/suspension.png 256w,\n/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/ccc41/suspension.png 512w,\n/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/b5658/suspension.png 1024w","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/22bfc/suspension.webp 256w,\n/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/d689f/suspension.webp 512w,\n/static/77170f41321f5406b485f2594c6da8d7/67ded/suspension.webp 1024w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"}]},"width":1024,"height":1024}}}}},"relatedPosts":{"nodes":[]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/submission/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"submission meaning and examples"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blunder/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"blunder meaning and examples"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"25f2934c-b1a3-5151-95a1-d524601f6643","previousPostId":"69bb026c-35fb-5f36-b134-0cc8c7c72b70","nextPostId":"13b53145-fc5f-5e76-abb4-4d97f9608447","relatedPosts":[]}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}